<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Fidget Spinners.</title>
    <!-- <link href="assets/css/styles.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"> -->
    <style>
      <%- css %>
    </style>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="images/favicon.png">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width">
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="topbar">
      <h1>
        Fidget Spinners.
        <span>A big list of nice spinners</span>
      </h1>
      <ul>
        <li class="current">
          <a href="#">Spinners</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="filters">
      <span class="sort">
        <span class="js-sort-label label">Sort by...</span>
        <svg class="sort-icon" version="1.1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 444.819 444.819" xml:space="preserve">
          <path d="M434.252,114.203l-21.409-21.416c-7.419-7.04-16.084-10.561-25.975-10.561c-10.095,0-18.657,3.521-25.7,10.561
          L222.41,231.549L83.653,92.791c-7.042-7.04-15.606-10.561-25.697-10.561c-9.896,0-18.559,3.521-25.979,10.561l-21.128,21.416
          C3.615,121.436,0,130.099,0,140.188c0,10.277,3.619,18.842,10.848,25.693l185.864,185.865c6.855,7.23,15.416,10.848,25.697,10.848
          c10.088,0,18.75-3.617,25.977-10.848l185.865-185.865c7.043-7.044,10.567-15.608,10.567-25.693
          C444.819,130.287,441.295,121.629,434.252,114.203z">
        </svg>
        <select class="js-sort-select">
          <option value="">Sort by...</option>
          <option value="added_newest">Sort by date added (Newest first)</option>
          <option value="added_oldest">Sort by date added (Oldest first)</option>
          <option value="price_asc">Sort by price ($ → $$)</option>
          <option value="price_desc">Sort by price ($$ → $)</option>
          <option value="name_az">Sort by name (A → Z)</option>
          <option value="name_za">Sort by name (Z → A)</option>
        </select>
      </span>
      <input class="js-search search" value="" type="text" placeholder="Search a model or brand...">
      <svg class="search-icon" version="1.1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 56.966 56.966" xml:space="preserve">
        <path d="M55.146,51.887L41.588,37.786c3.486-4.144,5.396-9.358,5.396-14.786c0-12.682-10.318-23-23-23s-23,10.318-23,23
        s10.318,23,23,23c4.761,0,9.298-1.436,13.177-4.162l13.661,14.208c0.571,0.593,1.339,0.92,2.162,0.92
        c0.779,0,1.518-0.297,2.079-0.837C56.255,54.982,56.293,53.08,55.146,51.887z M23.984,6c9.374,0,17,7.626,17,17s-7.626,17-17,17
        s-17-7.626-17-17S14.61,6,23.984,6z">
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="items js-items">
      <div class="noresults js-items-noresults">
        No results found.
      </div>
      <% items.map((item) => { %>
        <div
          class="item js-item"
          data-company="<%= item.brand.name %>"
          data-name="<%= item.name %>"
          data-price="<%= item.price %>"
          data-added="<%= item.added %>"
          data-search="<%= item.brand.name.toLowerCase() + ' ' + item.name.toLowerCase() %>"
        >
          <a class="pic-wrapper" href="images/spinners/<%= item.brand.id + '/' + item.file %>" target="_blank">
            <img
              class="pic js-lazy js-lazy-hidden"
              data-src-lazy="images/spinners/<%= item.brand.id + '/' + item.file.replace('.jpg', '_thumb.jpg') %>"
              src="images/placeholder.png"
              alt="<%= item.name %>"
            >
          </a>
          <div class="info">
            <a class="brand" href="<%= item.brand.url %>" target="_blank">
              <%= item.brand.name %>
            </a>
            <span class="name">
              <%= item.name %>
            </span>
            <% if (item.price != '-1') { %>
              <span class="price">
                <%= item.price %>$
              </span>
            <% } %>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% }) %>
    </div>
    <div class="faq" id="faq">
      <h2>FAQ</h2>
      <h3>What are those weird tiny objects? What is this site?</h3>
      <p>
        <a href="https://www.forbes.com/sites/jplafke/2016/12/23/fidget-spinners-are-the-must-have-office-toy-for-2017/#693cc3ee18a4" target="_blank">
          Fidget Spinners Are The Must-Have Office Toy For 2017
        </a> - Forbes
      </p>
      <p>
        This page is a showcase of high-quality spinners, made with noble materials.<br>
      </p>
      <h3>The list is not up to date, I found an error. What should I do?</h3>
      <p>
        This list is being updated regularly.
        It (should) feature original spinners only, that is why plastic spinners or Amazon clones are missing.<br>
        That being said, if you find a mistake, or if you know good quality plastic spinners that should appear in this list, feel free to contact me! (see below)<br>
        If you have web development knowledge, you can also check the project <a href="https://github.com/johansatge/fidget-spinners.net" target="_blank">on Github</a>.
      </p>
      <h3 id="contact">I would like to contact you.</h3>
      <p>
        You can do so on <a href="https://twitter.com/fidgetspinners_" target="_blank">Twitter</a>
        or <a href="mailto:info@fidget-spinners.net" target="_blank">by email</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      Made with &hearts; in France - <a href="https://github.com/johansatge/fidget-spinners.net" target="_blank">Source code</a>
    </div>
    <!--<script src="assets/js/scripts.js"></script>-->
    <script>
      <%- js %>
    </script>
    <script>
      App.init()
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
